Xi Jinping, general secretary of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee, has stressed sense of mission and dedication among Party officials and young people in an instruction honoring late village official Huang Wenxiu. Xi, also Chinese president and chairman of the Central Military Commission, grieved over Huang's death and extended condolences to her family. 
